metadata/attribute_title = "Dark Dwarf Heritage"
metadata/attribute_description = "Your soot colored skin indicates you hail from the ash covered lands of Dun Mortis. Your kind are known by your paler skinned cousins as the Dark Dwarves, a race cast away from the light of the All-father into the refuge bin of Stonebeard's furnace. You are hated by your kin as an oathbreaker by virtue of your birthright and if you attempt to enter into their holds will likely be killed on sight."

